262
00:21:44,768 --> 00:21:47,950
where I don't know if I want to do this anymore.

263
00:21:48,890 --> 00:21:52,833
But in my darkest moments, I am thankful for my support network,

264
00:21:52,833 --> 00:21:56,655
for my mom, for my friends who remind me that every failure,

265
00:21:56,655 --> 00:22:02,718
every setback, and every difficult day is an opportunity to grow

266
00:22:02,718 --> 00:22:04,779
